{
  "appsettings": {
    "loglevel": "debug",
    "namespace": "@Model.Name"
  },
  "_note": "The live database connection AND the Auth0 inbound audience for this 'scriptagent' service (see common::auth0 and docs/auth0-m2m.md) are read at runtime from ~/.@(Model.Name).json by the common Config loader -- add an 'auth0' section there (domain, audiences.scriptagent), not here. ScriptAgent never calls another service, so it has no M2M client of its own. The ScriptAgent binds to the first free port in 5100-5200 and self-registers in core.server_node as an Agent node."
}
